His friends turned a cold shoulder to him when they knew the police inter­
rogated him./The intelligence agency has turned a cold shoulder to its col­
laborators and left them to face their fate on their own./Sheba was a kingdom 
that was abandoned by nature and left at the mercy of the sands of the desert. 
